</style><p>这次，光野木吉尔就是日下部<em>梓的未经证实的传闻是在光野木首播后出现的</em>，理由<em>是“角色设计的发型很像日下部梓</em>”。</p><p> ANYCOLOR（旗下运营着VTuber团体虹山寺等）运营的虚拟人才学院（VTA）自8月以来不断传出丑闻，导致大量成员离开公司，但日下部梓却是该团体第2代成员，并在1月9日（这被认为是他是否会在虹山寺出道或被开除的一个征兆），发行档案被设为私人，这表明上述丑闻可能已经发生。两者之间有直接关系。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="QrvF8z0DrY"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-training-project-virtual-talent-academy-by-anycolor-of-nijisanji-19-out-of-29-students-disappeared/">Nijisanji运营的ANYCOLOR VTuber培训项目29名成员中有19人失踪</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nijisanji 运营的 ANYCOLOR VTuber 培训项目的 29 名成员中，有 19 人失踪” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-training-project-virtual-talent-academy-by-anycolor-of-nijisanji-19-out-of-29-students-disappeared/embed/#?secret=pmg4X29SM8#?secret=QrvF8z0DrY" data-secret="QrvF8z0DrY" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="i8T0NwpO6G"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/virtual-talent-academy-vta-x-official-account-disappears-tag-supporting-vta-etc/">“#VTA Supporting”等从 Virtual Talent Academy (VTA) X 官方账号中消失</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="““#VTA Supporting”等从 Virtual Talent Academy (VTA) X 官方账号中消失” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/virtual-talent-academy-vta-x-official-account-disappears-tag-supporting-vta-etc/embed/#?secret=dYcE1L0TvU#?secret=i8T0NwpO6G" data-secret="i8T0NwpO6G" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">以上信息并不能100%确认Jill Mitsunogi就是Azusa Kusakabe。</span> “相似的声音等”并不能证明他们是同一个人。因此，目前属于不确定谣言的范围，请您不要做出任何可能给艺人、经纪公司或团体带来麻烦的行为或诽谤。 </p><p></p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Rf73opVJ9N"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/uncertain-rumors-abound-that-new-vtuber-ryugahama-yue-may-be-kusunoki-sio-who-has-been-on-hiatus-for-about-3-years/">新人VTuber Ryugahama Ue 有不确定的传言称她是停摆约3年的“Kusu Shiorizakura”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“新 VTuber Ryugahama Ae 有不确定的传言称她是已经停播约 3 年的 Kusunoki Sakura” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/uncertain-rumors-abound-that-new-vtuber-ryugahama-yue-may-be-kusunoki-sio-who-has-been-on-hiatus-for-about-3-years/embed/#?secret=J9tEmbGX5f#?secret=Rf73opVJ9N" data-secret="Rf73opVJ9N" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@JILLMITSUNOKI" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">吉尔·三木 / 吉尔</a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@JILLMITSUNOKI" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">·三木 / 吉尔·三木</a>/ <a href="https://riot-music.com/artist/jill-mitsunoki/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="吉尔·三乃木">吉尔·三木</a></p><cite>YouTube / X（推特）/ RIOT MUSIC</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp 经营代表“Mr.2（暂定）”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber 信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/uncertain-rumor-circulating-that-riot-music-new-vtuber-mitsunoki-jill-may-be-a-virtual-talent-academy-vta-kusakabe-azusa/">后新 VTuber Jill Mitsunogi Virtual Talent Academy (VTA) 不确定的谣言正在流传，她是“Azusa Kusakabe”，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/uncertain-rumor-circulate-that-riot-music-new-vtuber-mitsunoki-jill-may-be-a-virtual-talent-academy-vta-kusakabe-azusa/feed/ 0 103927
